Ping Monitor - LXDE panel plugin that execute a script by timer event or by left click on panel item. 
It can be used to monitor status of any process, event or action (ex. IP address ping).

Usage:
	Just specify executable script path is Script field and its parameters in Args field.
	Example of the script file you can find in 'examples' folder.
	
Config example:
	Field                        Value
	-------                      -----------
	Text                         TUNNEL #3
	Label width on panel         15
	Run script every (seconds)   60
	Stop timer                   
	Script path                  ~/bin/ip-tun.sh
	Script args                  tun3 FF0000 FFFF00